r charts are as follows. Data for bar chart 1. U, 4 units; k sub 1, 0 units; k sub 2, 0 units. Data for bar chart 2. U, 0 units; k sub 1, 2 units; k sub 2, 2 units.\" height=\"71\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH949191.g12.png\" width=\"300\"></span></p>\n"],"answer":3}]